descriptionHtml:
Hello,
this is the preset of one of the characters i created.
She is called Anine, sure you can rename her to whatever you want.

---> All the information you need to know you can get from the Picture (Mods)<---

Just treat her well :)
I wanted to publish her, because I'll maybe quit skyrim, so everyone can use these presets if he likes too and I can also get it back if i want to continue playing skyrim sometime again.

The credits go to all the authors of the mods used on her and also a big thanks to the author of Racemenu, without this it woudn't have been possible.
